document_data.Trivia:
*According to [[Elminster]] of [[Shadowdale]], [[gorgon]]s' breath had a strong smell of stewed cabbage.{{Cite dragon/97/Ecology of the Gorgon|25}}
*Cabbages were part of a group of common vegetables that those in [[northwest Faerûn]] referred to as "fieldings."{{Cite dragon/277/The New Adventures of Volo: Dragonwing Stew|94}}
*[[Tressym]] could not stand the smell of burnt cabbage and it could be used as an effective repellent.{{cite web| url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190913214112/http://www.candlekeep.com/library/articles/sse/sse_040506-08.htm| title = So Saith Ed Apr – Jun 2008| accessdate = 25-11-2021| date = 25-11-2021}}
